{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"e799bfa84a","title":"关于部队支左的指示","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"05ef0338bb","index":0,"year":1967,"month":4,"day":null,"articleId":"e799bfa84a"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"70a1e48626","name":"军队支左","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"877762393f","name":"两条路线斗争","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"eb87a9588f","name":"四川文革","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","name":"毛泽东思想万岁（1961年-1968年）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives3/main/45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"187dd2039a","type":"paragraph","text":"对《爱国主义还是卖国主义？》","index":0,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"16302b9567","type":"paragraph","text":"一文所加的一段哥","index":1,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"b4d25167f6","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":2,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"7138893870","type":"paragraph","text":"究竟是中国组织义和团跑到欧美、日本帝国主义国家去造反、去“杀人放火”呢？还是各帝国主义国家跑到中国这块地方来侵略中国、压道和刺削中国人民，因而激趣中国人民群众奋起反抗帝国主义及其在中国的走狗、负官、污束？这是大是大非问题，不可不辩论清楚。","index":3,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"7b23ee81f6","type":"paragraph","text":"关于部队支左的指示","index":4,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"af82a3175b","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":5,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"f528d43492","type":"paragraph","text":"军队的威信必须坚决维护，不能有牛点含糊。拥军爱民社论的发表是当前工作的中心。军队第一次支左、支工、支农、军训、军管是大规模的战斗任务，犯错误是难免的，问题在于当前主要危险是有人把解放军打下去。","index":6,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"b2fd26fb28","type":"paragraph","text":"XX","index":7,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"cf62eaa3f6","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":8,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"745e9abda9","type":"paragraph","text":"支左支错，支到保守派方向去，改过来就行了，允许的。我们在这五大工作中，三分之二做对了，三分之一做错了，就是很好了。","index":9,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"0c1e8510a5","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":10,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"add2c188d4","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":11,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"1876c7e1c2","type":"paragraph","text":"X","index":12,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"cdb253c28c","type":"paragraph","text":"有的受老婆孩子观点的影响，有的是县委地委或地委书记，他们的孩子是那个地方的保守派，或者是老婆是那个地方当权派之一，这是值得我们警惕的。","index":13,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"0f6bed9380","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自谢富治付总理四月六日讲话）关于四川交化大革命的指示","index":14,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"54dffbfe6e","type":"paragraph","text":"（一九六七年四月）","index":15,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"c78f93c3fa","type":"paragraph","text":"从宜宾问题的揭发，才开始揭开了四川阶级斗争盖子的序幕，才开始揭开李井泉的盖子。四川文化大革命之所以困难，主要是刘、邓、李井泉搞的，他们把刘结挺打成反革命，把他们开除出党，这次才翻过来。以后要把这个材料印出来，发给每个党员。四川阶级斗争的揭盖子，两条路线斗争还未解决。","index":16,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"e38d8fdf31","type":"paragraph","text":"（摘自林彪同志1967年4月5日关于四川问题的讲话）","index":17,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"},{"id":"9a0298bd5c","type":"paragraph","text":"·299。","index":18,"publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a"}],"page":{"id":"2b54c56935","publicationId":"45f85d41-2767-49bc-87e9-ba331b429fce","articleId":"e799bfa84a","start":312,"end":312}}}},"__N_SSG":true}